cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper combines reinforcement learning with deep learning, specifically using deep Q-networks and the options framework for hierarchical reinforcement learning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
